{"tid":1636234,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"呢場喺一場符號之戰！！！","createTime":"2019-10-07T17:14:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T17:22:29.000Z","uid":263443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c1285f211258426b25b4bb96aea2ed39b009e5a2","tid":1636234,"uid":263443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:14:50.000Z","msg":"多得反蒙面法<br />\n令到我哋示威可以史無前例咁方便、咁日常、咁低成本<br />\n所有人，應承我<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">從今日開始，日日都係口罩日！！！！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋必須要爭奪呢個符號<br />\n呢個代表不服從、逆權、抗命嘅符號<br />\n試下幻想下，如果喺條街，帶口罩嘅人仲多過唔帶口罩嘅人<br />\n藍絲、中間派個腦就會hand晒機：<span style=\"color: gold;\">屌，點L解仲有咁多人支持班暴徒㗎？？？</span><br />\n就算多唔過都好，只要帶口罩嘅人比立法之前多，都已經係一種示威<br />\n<br />\n而且，根據7婆條ON9反蒙面法<br />\n平日帶口罩係<span style=\"color: gold;\">完完全全唔犯法</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">從今日開始，人人出街帶口罩！！！<br />\n人人都係流動嘅文宣！！！<br />\n讓抗命嘅符號無處理在！！！</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a671031b41439cf547f6591016360abf993dfdb6","tid":1636234,"uid":286549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:22:29.000Z","msg":"全民口罩 日日都戴！"}]}